    %p The Account API allows you to request the verification pin from your user and send to us for validation.

    .note.note-danger
      %strong Note:
      This is a <a href="/sections/api/authorization.html">Bearer Authorized</a> call.

    %table.arguments
      %thead
        %tr
          %th Parameter
          %th Required
          %th Type
          %th Description
      %tbody

        %tr
          %td.param client_id
          %td.required.yes yes
          %td.format String
          %td.description The client id issued to your Sign2Pay Client Application.

        %tr
          %td.param verification_pin
          %td.required.yes yes
          %td.format String
          %td.description The Verification Pin that was sent to your user in the remarks field of the â‚¬0.01 transfer we made to their account.

